===游戏引擎===
{{main|Decima (游戏引擎)}}
在其{{le|杀戮地带：暗影坠落|Killzone Shadow Fall}}发售后，游戏信息内声称为一款自有的未命名引擎开发；之后于2015年6月，宣布《地平线：零之曙光》的引擎与《杀戮地带：暗影坠落》相同<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://gamingbolt.com/horizon-zero-dawn-is-1080p30fps-and-uses-modified-killzone-shadowfall-engine|title=Horizon: Zero Dawn Is 1080p/30fps And Uses Modified Killzone: Shadowfall Engine|last=VanDervoot|first=Oliver|date=June 19, 2015|work=GamingBolt|access-date=December 3, 2016|via=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180813162418/https://gamingbolt.com/horizon-zero-dawn-is-1080p30fps-and-uses-modified-killzone-shadowfall-engine|archive-date=2018-08-13|dead-url=yes}}{{en}}</ref>。

Guerrilla Games董事Hermen Hulst在PlayStation Experience 2016的说法，Decima具备构建人工智能（AI）、物理效果和逻辑的工具和功能，以及用于创建整个游戏世界的资源库<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2016/12/03/death-stranding-will-run-on-the-decima-engine-developed-by-guerrilla-games|title=PSX 2016: Death Stranding Will Run on Guerrilla Games' Decima Engine|last=Rad|first=Chloi|date=December 3, 2016|work=[[IGN|IGN]]|access-date=December 3, 2016|via=|archive-date=2018-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180813164810/http://www.ign.com/articles/2016/12/03/death-stranding-will-run-on-the-decima-engine-developed-by-guerrilla-games|dead-url=no}}{{en}}</ref>Decima引擎发布将原生支持[[4K解析度|4K解析度]]与[[高动态范围成像|HDR]]。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/kojima-partnering-with-killzone-horizon-dev-guerri/1100-6445954/|title=Kojima Partnering With Killzone, Horizon Dev Guerrilla for Death Stranding|last=Pereira|first=Chris|date=December 3, 2016|work=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|access-date=December 3, 2016|via=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]]|archive-date=2018-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180813165517/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/kojima-partnering-with-killzone-horizon-dev-guerri/1100-6445954/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 引擎以日本江户时期的人工岛[[出島|出島]]命名（拼写为Dejima），正是17世纪时荷兰商馆所在地。
